  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK531">
<l>iṟanta vekuḷiyiṟ ṟītē ciṟanta </l>
<l> vuvakai makiḻcciyiṟ cōrvu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>More evil than excessive anger, is forgetfulness which springs from the intoxication of great joy.</l>
            </lg>
